canceled.

04:09.825 --> 04:11.733
Oh, um...

04:11.827 --> 04:14.920
I thought
we could grill tonight.

04:15.071 --> 04:17.405
Okay. Sure.

04:17.424 --> 04:19.591
Oh.

04:28.010 --> 04:29.493
Gotcha.

04:29.511 --> 04:31.728
Empty.

04:32.831 --> 04:35.565
What set off the traps?

04:51.608 --> 04:53.709
You're not watering today?

04:54.962 --> 04:57.462
