05:25.567 --> 05:27.884
Benjamin, what the hell
are you doing?!

05:27.903 --> 05:30.329
Finally getting rid
of the rodent.

05:32.482 --> 05:33.648
Was that another explosion?

05:33.667 --> 05:35.167
You're asking the wrong person.

05:35.318 --> 05:37.669
<i> NOAH: Ma'am, did I just hear</i>
<i> another explosion?</i>

05:37.821 --> 05:39.153
-Ma'am?
<i> -Yes.</i>

05:39.173 --> 05:41.398
It's my husband. He's trying
to destroy the backyard.

05:41.416 --> 05:42.990
-Ma'am...
<i> -BENJAMIN: Who are you</i>
<i> on the phone with?</i>

05:43.085 --> 05:45.085
