shock and awe on a gopher.

06:10.019 --> 06:12.445
-I don't know if he's hurt
or not.
-The gopher?

06:12.598 --> 06:14.598
-No. Not the gopher.
-Holly, get them out of here.

06:14.691 --> 06:16.950
Is that your husband?
He seems pretty banged up.

06:17.102 --> 06:18.451
No, not him.

06:18.545 --> 06:20.045
Hey, Cap?

06:20.196 --> 06:22.288
Don't call me that.

06:22.365 --> 06:23.940
Ma'am.

06:24.033 --> 06:26.610
Exactly who do you think
is hurt here?

06:26.703 --> 06:28.278
My neighbor.

06:28.296 --> 06:29.946
Gary.

06:29.965 --> 06:31.556
HEN:
His house looks fine.

06:31.783 --> 06:33.466
