cameras everywhere.

07:33.528 --> 07:35.787
All right, Chimney,
see if you can access

07:35.956 --> 07:38.031
-the tunnel from inside.
-Copy that, Cap.

07:38.125 --> 07:40.183
-Uh, sorry.
-Buck, start digging up
out here.

07:40.185 --> 07:43.110
