and by hearing me sing it...

12:07.135 --> 12:08.876
It got him to pay attention.

12:08.895 --> 12:10.787
I wish I could listen
to more calls.

12:10.805 --> 12:12.305
Didn't they give you samples
at the academy?

12:12.399 --> 12:14.290
